snippet.title: Sopa - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description: Get another look at Sopa in this latest trailer for the upcoming narrative adventure game about the things we pass along, including a look at its rich world, characters, and more. Sopa will be available in 2024.
